<body>

	<div id="side">
		<br>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<h3>호스트 페이지</h3><br>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a class="function" href="/host/hostInfo.mobiil">정보 조회</a><br><br>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a class="function" href="/host/hostModifyView.mobiil">정보 수정</a><br><br>
